### 3. UI/Layout — No se encontraron problemas

- El único uso de `MediaQuery.sizeOf()` en [home_screen.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/views/screens/home_screen.dart) (línea 24-25) verifica `size.height < 400` para ajustar tamaño de personajes. Esto es correcto: funciona en portrait y no intenta adaptar a landscape.
- El único `LayoutBuilder` en [progress_widgets.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/widgets/progress_widgets.dart) (línea 48) se usa para obtener `constraints.maxWidth` del contenedor padre para la barra de progreso. Correcto, no depende de orientación.
- No se encontraron `OrientationBuilder`, `OrientationMode`, ni lógica de detección de landscape en ningún archivo.

---

## 🟡 Objetivo Secundario: Limpieza de Errores y Optimización

### 4. [lib/main.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/main.dart) — Código muerto eliminado

**Error**: El método `_errorRoute()` (línea 126-128) nunca era llamado — [_onGenerateRoute](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/main.dart#96-119) usa directamente [_errorWidget()](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/main.dart#120-126).

```diff
-  Route<dynamic> _errorRoute() {
-    return MaterialPageRoute(builder: (_) => _errorWidget());
-  }
```

### 5. Niveles 1-4 — Casts redundantes con `as ProfileNotifier`

| Archivo | Línea | Cambio |
|---------|-------|--------|
| [level1_screen.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/views/levels/level1/level1_screen.dart) | 76 | `ref.read(...) as ProfileNotifier` → `ref.read(...)` |
| [level2_screen.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/views/levels/level2/level2_screen.dart) | 79, 86 | Igual |
| [level3_screen.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/views/levels/level3/level3_screen.dart) | 80, 109 | Igual |
| [level4_screen.dart](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/views/levels/level4/level4_screen.dart) | 46, 53 | Igual |

**Porqué era un error**: `currentProfileProvider` ya está tipado como `NotifierProvider<ProfileNotifier, ChildProfile?>`. El `ref.read(...notifier)` devuelve [ProfileNotifier](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/providers/app_providers.dart#11-77) directamente. El cast `as ProfileNotifier` es redundante y arriesgado — si la jerarquía de tipos cambia, generaría un `TypeError` en runtime en vez de un error de compilación.

```diff:level1_screen.dart
import 'package:confetti/confetti.dart';
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:flutter_animate/flutter_animate.dart';
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
import 'package:isla_digital/core/theme/app_theme.dart';
import 'package:isla_digital/presentation/providers/app_providers.dart'; // FIX: Importado para acceder a los providers
import 'package:isla_digital/presentation/widgets/glass_container.dart';
import 'package:isla_digital/presentation/widgets/island_background.dart';
import 'package:isla_digital/presentation/widgets/progress_widgets.dart';
import 'package:isla_digital/presentation/widgets/safe_lottie.dart';

class Level1Screen extends ConsumerStatefulWidget {
  const Level1Screen({super.key});

  @override
  ConsumerState<Level1Screen> createState() => _Level1ScreenState();
}

class _Level1ScreenState extends ConsumerState<Level1Screen> {
  int currentStep = 0;
  late ConfettiController _confettiController;
  final PageController _pageController = PageController();

  final List<Map<String, dynamic>> steps = [
    {
      'title': '¡Hola, Amiguito!',
      'instruction': 'Toca el botón brillante para despertar la isla',
      'icon': Icons.power_settings_new,
      'lottie': 'assets/animations/ui/power.json',
      'color': IslaColors.oceanBlue,
    },
    {
      'title': '¡Abre el Tesoro!',
      'instruction': 'Desliza hacia arriba como una ola saltarina',
      'icon': Icons.expand_less,
      'lottie': 'assets/animations/ui/swipe_up.json',
      'color': IslaColors.sunflower,
    },
    {
      'title': '¡Cuida tu Isla!',
      'instruction': 'Toca el escudo para proteger tu tesoro digital',
      'icon': Icons.security,
      'lottie': 'assets/animations/ui/shield.json',
      'color': IslaColors.jungleGreen,
    },
  ];

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _confettiController = ConfettiController(duration: const Duration(seconds: 3));
  }

  @override
  void dispose() {
    _confettiController.dispose();
    _pageController.dispose();
    super.dispose();
  }

  void _onStepCompleted() {
    if (currentStep < steps.length - 1) {
      setState(() => currentStep++);
      _pageController.nextPage(
        duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 600),
        curve: Curves.easeOutBack,
      );
    } else {
      _finishLevel();
    }
  }

  /// FIX: Lógica para desbloquear el siguiente nivel y mostrar celebración
  void _finishLevel() {
    // Desbloqueamos el Nivel 2 en el perfil del usuario
    final notifier = ref.read(currentProfileProvider.notifier) as ProfileNotifier;
    notifier.unlockLevel(2);
    notifier.addBadge('explorer_level_1');
    
    _showFinalCelebration();
  }

  void _showFinalCelebration() {
    _confettiController.play();
    showDialog(
      context: context,
      barrierDismissible: false,
      builder: (context) => AlertDialog(
        backgroundColor: Colors.white.withValues(alpha: 0.95),
        shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(32)),
        title: Text(
          '¡ERES UN SUPERHÉROE!',
          textAlign: TextAlign.center,
          style: IslaThemes.titleMediumStyle.copyWith(color: IslaColors.oceanDark),
        ),
        content: Column(
          mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min,
          children: [
            const SafeLottie(
              path: 'assets/animations/success/pearl.json',
            ),
            const SizedBox(height: 16),
            Text(
              '¡Ganaste la Perla de Sabiduría!',
              textAlign: TextAlign.center,
              style: IslaThemes.subtitleStyle,
            ),
          ],
        ),
        actions: [
          Center(
            child: ElevatedButton(
              onPressed: () {
                Navigator.pop(context); 
                Navigator.pop(context); 
              },
              child: const Text('VOLVER AL MAPA'),
            ).animate().shimmer(delay: 500.ms, duration: 1500.ms),
          )
        ],
      ),
    );
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    // Validamos que el índice no se pase por si acaso
    final safeStep = currentStep.clamp(0, steps.length - 1);
    
    return Scaffold(
      body: Stack(
        alignment: Alignment.center,
        children: [
          IslandBackground(
            child: SafeArea(
              child: Column(
                children: [
                  _buildHeader(safeStep),
                  const SizedBox(height: 8),
                  Padding(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 40),
                    child: StepIndicator(
                      currentStep: safeStep,
                      totalSteps: steps.length,
                      activeColor: steps[safeStep]['color'] as Color,
                    ),
                  ),
                  const SizedBox(height: 16),
                  Expanded(
                    child: PageView.builder(
                      controller: _pageController,
                      physics: const NeverScrollableScrollPhysics(),
                      itemCount: steps.length,
                      itemBuilder: (context, index) => _buildStep(steps[index]),
                    ),
                  ),
                ],
              ),
            ),
          ),
          ConfettiWidget(
            confettiController: _confettiController,
            blastDirectionality: BlastDirectionality.explosive,
            colors: const [
              IslaColors.oceanBlue, 
              IslaColors.sunflower, 
              IslaColors.jungleGreen, 
              IslaColors.sunsetPink
            ],
          ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildHeader(int step) {
    return Padding(
      padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16, vertical: 20),
      child: Row(
        children: [
          IconButton(
            icon: const Icon(Icons.close_rounded, color: IslaColors.oceanDark, size: 32),
            onPressed: () => Navigator.pop(context),
          ),
          const Spacer(),
          Text(
            'PASO ${step + 1} DE ${steps.length}',
            style: IslaThemes.labelStyle.copyWith(
              color: IslaColors.charcoal.withValues(alpha: 0.5),
            ),
          ),
          const Spacer(),
          const SizedBox(width: 48),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildStep(Map<String, dynamic> step) {
    final color = step['color'] as Color;
    
    return Padding(
      padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 24, vertical: 12),
      child: Column(
        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
        children: [
          Text(
            step['title'] as String,
            style: IslaThemes.displayStyle.copyWith(color: IslaColors.oceanDark),
            textAlign: TextAlign.center,
          ).animate().fadeIn().scale(curve: Curves.easeOutBack),
          
          const SizedBox(height: 40),
          
          GestureDetector(
            onTap: _onStepCompleted,
            child: Stack(
              alignment: Alignment.center,
              children: [
                Container(
                  width: 200,
                  height: 200,
                  decoration: BoxDecoration(
                    shape: BoxShape.circle,
                    color: color.withValues(alpha: 0.1),
                  ),
                ).animate(onPlay: (c) => c.repeat(reverse: true))
                 .scale(begin: const Offset(1, 1), end: const Offset(1.1, 1.1), duration: 2.seconds),
                 
                SafeLottie(
                  path: step['lottie'] as String,
                  backupIcon: step['icon'] as IconData,
                  size: 160,
                ),
              ],
            ),
          ).animate().fadeIn(delay: 300.ms).moveY(begin: 20, end: 0),
          
          const SizedBox(height: 50),
          
          GlassContainer(
            child: Text(
              step['instruction'] as String,
              textAlign: TextAlign.center,
              style: IslaThemes.subtitleStyle.copyWith(color: IslaColors.charcoal),
            ),
          ).animate().fadeIn(delay: 600.ms).slideY(begin: 0.2, end: 0),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
