- `unnecessary_lambdas`: [() { onProgress(); }](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/main.dart#19-48) → `onProgress` (tearoff)
- `use_decorated_box`: [Container(decoration: ...)](file:///home/l/Desktop/v0.4.0/lib/presentation/widgets/glass_container.dart#4-66) → `DecoratedBox(decoration: ...)` (más eficiente, no genera layer innecesaria)

